        <mo>&lt;</mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mn>1</mn>
            <mn>2</mn>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\textstyle \left|{\frac {\p=
si ^{n}}{\sqrt {5}}}\right|&lt;{\frac {1}{2}}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/2f36056259148225cdc34612e19c42887fb89055" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -1.838ex; width:9.077ex; height:4.843ex;" alt=3D"{\textstyle \left|=
{\frac {\psi ^{n}}{\sqrt {5}}}\right|&lt;{\frac {1}{2}}}"></span> for all <=
span class=3D"texhtml"><i>n</i> =E2=89=A5 0</span>, the number <span class=
=3D"texhtml"><i>F</i><sub><i>n</i></sub></span> is the closest <a href=3D"h=
ttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Integer" title=3D"Integer">integer</a> to <spa=
n class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-mat=
h-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=
=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle {\frac {\=
varphi ^{n}}{\sqrt {5}}}}">
