      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <msup>
              <mi>=CF=86<!-- =CF=86 --></mi>
              <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                <mi>n</mi>
              </mrow>
            </msup>
            <msqrt>
              <mn>5</mn>
            </msqrt>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle {\frac {\varp=
hi ^{n}}{\sqrt {5}}}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/67180162747d0e482d1bbb421cee2742f2e303c5" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -2.838ex; width:3.934ex; height:6.343ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle {\f=
rac {\varphi ^{n}}{\sqrt {5}}}}"></span>. Therefore, it can be found by <a =
href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rounding" title=3D"Rounding">rounding=
</a>, using the nearest integer function:
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
splay=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
