(F)=3D\left\lfloor \log _{\varphi }{\sqrt {5}}F\right\rceil ,\ F\geq 1.}"><=
/span>
</p><p>Instead using the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Floor_fun=
ction" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Floor function">floor function</a> gi=
ves the largest index of a Fibonacci number that is not greater than <span =
class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">F</span>:
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
