<p>Binet's formula provides a proof that a positive integer <span class=3D"=
texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">x</span> is a Fibonacci number <=
a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/If_and_only_if" title=3D"If and onl=
y if">if and only if</a> at least one of <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mw=
e-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathm=
l-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math=
