^{\infty }{\frac {1}{F_{2k-1}}}=3D{\frac {\sqrt {5}}{4}}\;\vartheta _{2}\!\=
left(0,{\frac {3-{\sqrt {5}}}{2}}\right)^{2},}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
