heta _{2}\!\left(0,{\frac {3-{\sqrt {5}}}{2}}\right)^{2},}"></span>
</p><p>and the sum of squared reciprocal Fibonacci numbers as
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
