rtheta _{2}\!\left(0,{\frac {3-{\sqrt {5}}}{2}}\right)^{4}-\vartheta _{4}\!=
\left(0,{\frac {3-{\sqrt {5}}}{2}}\right)^{4}+1\right).}"></span>
</p><p>If we add 1 to each Fibonacci number in the first sum, there is also=
 the closed form
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
splay=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
isplaystyle \sum _{k=3D1}^{\infty }{\frac {1}{1+F_{2k-1}}}=3D{\frac {\sqrt =
{5}}{2}},}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <munderover>
          <mo>=E2=88=91<!-- =E2=88=91 --></mo>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>k</mi>
            <mo>=3D</mo>
            <mn>1</mn>
          </mrow>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi mathvariant=3D"normal">=E2=88=9E<!-- =E2=88=9E --></mi>
          </mrow>
        </munderover>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mn>1</mn>
            <mrow>
              <mn>1</mn>
              <mo>+</mo>
              <msub>
                <mi>F</mi>
                <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mn>2</mn>
                  <mi>k</mi>
                  <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
                  <mn>1</mn>
                </mrow>
              </msub>
            </mrow>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <msqrt>
              <mn>5</mn>
            </msqrt>
            <mn>2</mn>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
        <mo>,</mo>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle \sum _{k=3D1}=
^{\infty }{\frac {1}{1+F_{2k-1}}}=3D{\frac {\sqrt {5}}{2}},}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
