sum _{k=3D1}^{\infty }{\frac {1}{1+F_{2k-1}}}=3D{\frac {\sqrt {5}}{2}},}"><=
/span>
</p><p>and there is a <i>nested</i> sum of squared Fibonacci numbers giving=
 the reciprocal of the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Golden_rati=
o" title=3D"Golden ratio">golden ratio</a>,
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
splay=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
isplaystyle \sum _{k=3D1}^{\infty }{\frac {(-1)^{k+1}}{\sum _{j=3D1}^{k}{F_=
{j}}^{2}}}=3D{\frac {{\sqrt {5}}-1}{2}}.}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
