gle</a>:<sup id=3D"cite_ref-FOOTNOTELucas18917_68-0" class=3D"reference"><a=
 href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fibonacci_sequence#cite_note-FOOTNOT=
ELucas18917-68"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>66<span class=3D"cite-=
bracket">]</span></a></sup>
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
