as <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zeckendorf%27s_theorem" title=
=3D"Zeckendorf's theorem">Zeckendorf's theorem</a>, and a sum of Fibonacci =
numbers that satisfies these conditions is called a Zeckendorf representati=
on. The Zeckendorf representation of a number can be used to derive its <a =
href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fibonacci_coding" title=3D"Fibonacci =
coding">Fibonacci coding</a>.</li>
