tle=3D"Right triangle">right triangle</a> with integer sides, or in other w=
ords, the largest number in a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pyth=
agorean_triple" title=3D"Pythagorean triple">Pythagorean triple</a>, obtain=
